{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "战火之霸道 第12章 3-3 王权",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "面对千钧一发的危机，\\n王子向谢斯提出交易，\\n成功劝退了谢斯军。另一方面，\\n莱昂尼多军正为攻陷圣城而进军。\\n王子一行人为守护圣城而紧追敌人。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "我们被彻底包围了……\\n这下……可不妙啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "哎呀，没想到你们还挺努力的呢。\\n不过，这只是时间问题。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "谢斯姐姐！等一下！\\n现在的状况是谢斯姐姐\\n也不愿意看到的吧！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "你想说什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "谢斯姐姐的目的，\\n是让我出面对抗魔神吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "凯特西",
            "context": "哎呀，被看穿了喵。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "既然如此，现在我和姐姐争斗，\\n消耗彼此的兵力并没有意义。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我不会要求你出手相助，\\n但姐姐应该也没必要\\n和魔神站在同一战线上。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "没必要？\\n不，我有必要站在这边。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你说什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "我之所以站在魔神这边，\\n是因为魔神做得并没有错。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "没、没有错！？\\n你是说魔神是对的吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "不管你们怎么想，对于民众来说，\\n塞西娅是由父王传位的\\n名正言顺的王。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "想要推翻名正言顺的王、\\n造成国家混乱的是你们。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "那只不过是表象！\\n其实……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "表象至关重要。\\n毕竟民众看到的就是表象。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "表象要有正当理由，\\n民众才能安心地顺从王。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "不努力安抚民心的王，\\n也配称作王吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "所以姐姐\\n才听命于魔神吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "没错。\\n至少我要称王的时候，\\n会让塞西娅传位给我。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我明白了……那么，\\n我们来做一笔交易吧，姐姐。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "交易？真没想到会从你嘴里\\n听到这个词。我很期待，\\n你究竟能拿出什么筹码呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "魔神由我来打倒。表面上看起来，\\n会是我夺走了塞西娅的王位吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "所以……到时候，\\n我会接受姐姐的讨伐。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "篡夺王位的叛徒，由你来讨伐。\\n这样一来，\\n你就是名正言顺的王了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "你说真的？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我的目的是救出塞西娅，\\n从魔神手上解救这个国家。\\n只要能办到这一点，我不会觊觎王位。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "凯特西",
            "context": "谢斯大人，怎么办喵？\\n一般来说这种说辞，\\n没人会信喵……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "恕我拒绝你提出的交易，\\n尤蒂尔。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "不过，为了确保后方的安全，\\n我们决定接下来前去压制\\n树海都市罗布雷尔。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "我感觉到罗布雷尔有谋反的预兆，\\n所以打算驻扎在罗布雷尔，\\n观察一段时间。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "我想想……我们应该会驻扎在那里\\n直到你们和莱昂尼多王兄的军队\\n决出胜负吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "谢斯姐姐……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "好了，我们走吧，凯特西。\\n要是不尽早攻下罗布雷尔，\\n我们会有危险的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "凯特西",
            "context": "哎呀……真是不坦率喵。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "姐姐……谢谢你……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "这样一来，就只剩大哥的军队了！\\n出发吧，尤蒂尔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "尤蒂尔，不好了。\\n莱昂尼多军正逼近圣城。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "看来他没有选择攻打我们，\\n而是选择了先攻下圣城！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "现在圣城里只有最低程度的防卫。\\n要是莱昂尼多军发起攻击，\\n怕是顶不住吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯，我们得抓紧时间\\n去追莱昂尼多哥哥！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "莱昂尼多军……吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "沙音？怎么了，你的脸色\\n看起来不是很好……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "抱歉……我没事。\\n只是想到了阁下……\\n不，莱昂尼多的事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "说起来……你以前\\n是莱昂尼多的手下呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "嗯……那个男人的确性格苛刻，\\n不顾及他人的想法，\\n也会为了目的而不择手段。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "但是……他是个自尊心极强的男人。\\n他拥有称霸天下的信念\\n和身为霸者的自负。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "哪怕只是暂时的，\\n我也不信他会向他人屈服。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "但哥哥他……曾经说过\\n拥有最强力量之人立于顶点\\n才是他所追求的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "那应该也不是假话。但是……\\n我觉得他似乎在为什么事\\n而倍感焦虑。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "焦虑？\\n莱昂尼多哥哥吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "嗯……虽然我不知道是什么事，\\n但他给我一种因为某些原因\\n才屈尊听从魔神命令的感觉。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "如果，是事出有因……\\n不，就算有原因也……可是……\\n抱歉，我组织不好语言。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "沙音，难道你……\\n想帮莱昂尼多哥哥吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "帮！？怎么可能！\\n不……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "曾经，莱昂尼多的确是\\n我的精神支柱……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "虽然最终我不过是他的一枚棋子，\\n但要是没有莱昂尼多，\\n我现在还不知道会怎么样……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "也许我是……觉得他对我有恩。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "不……抱歉，这个评价不适合\\n用来描述接下来要对战的敌人吧。\\n就当我没说吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "别在意。\\n我也跟你差不多。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我不赞同莱昂尼多哥哥的做法。\\n所以才会发展成现在这种\\n兵戎相见的场面。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "即便如此，\\n我也不会否定他的一切。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_04_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "他拥有很强的的意志力和行动力，\\n能做到我做不到的事……\\n我也很尊敬他。",
